the effect of this mysterious blood.



Summoning the stats panel, the King Fairy looks up the stats of the Growth talent. In his last life, he received no Growth talent when he took it.



[Growth (Taboo)] : Each level gains an additional stat point equal to the level.



Wang Xian's eyes suddenly widened, almost protruding out of her eyes, and she even rubbed her direct eyes to avoid being blinded.



As far as Wang Xian knows, THE LEVELS OF TALENTS are NORMAL, ELITE, Heavenly Arrogant, LEGENDARY, EPIC, and mythological, and he has never heard OF TABOO level talents.
